---
// src/pages/en/about-me.astro
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import euskal from '../../assets/euskal.jpeg'; 
---

<Layout title="About Me | Jorge - Developer & Maker">
    
    <section class="relative pt-32 pb-12 overflow-hidden bg-blue-50 dark:bg-gray-950">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[600px] h-[400px] bg-blue-400/20 blur-[120px] rounded-full -z-10 pointer-events-none"></div>
        
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6 text-center">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
                Beyond the <span class="text-blue-600">Code</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 dark:text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                A look at my journey, my learnings, and my technological vision.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-16 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 transition-colors duration-300">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
            
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-12">
                
                <div class="md:col-span-7 space-y-12">
                    
                    <div class="relative w-full max-w-md mx-auto md:mx-0 aspect-video rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl shadow-blue-500/20 border border-slate-200 dark:border-gray-800 mb-12 rotate-1 hover:rotate-0 transition-transform duration-500">
                        <Image 
                            src={euskal} 
                            alt="Photo of Jorge" 
                            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                        />
                    </div>

                    <div class="relative border-l-2 border-slate-200 dark:border-gray-800 ml-3 md:ml-6 space-y-16">
                        
                        <div class="relative pl-8 md:pl-12 group">
                            <span class="absolute -left-[9px] top-1 h-5 w-5 rounded-full border-4 border-white dark:border-gray-900 bg-blue-500 group-hover:bg-blue-400 transition-colors"></span>
                            
                            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Origin</h3>
                            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                                Since I was little, I've always been interested in knowing why things work. Technology, in particular, always seemed like magic to me: being able to talk to someone on the other side of the world, controlling a character in a video game...
                                In high school, that "magic" transformed into logic: I started to understand the <em>why</em> behind things.
                            </p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="relative pl-8 md:pl-12 group">
                            <span class="absolute -left-[9px] top-1 h-5 w-5 rounded-full border-4 border-white dark:border-gray-900 bg-blue-500 group-hover:bg-blue-400 transition-colors"></span>
                            
                            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">2018: Turning Point</h3>
                            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                                Building my first computer was the trigger. Seeing how physical components coordinated to execute complex applications seemed incredible to me. But the most fascinating thing was realizing that all of that had been designed by people like you and me. That's when I decided my path.
                            </p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="relative pl-8 md:pl-12 group">
                            <span class="absolute -left-[9px] top-1 h-5 w-5 rounded-full border-4 border-white dark:border-gray-900 bg-blue-500 group-hover:bg-blue-400 transition-colors"></span>
                            
                            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Maker as a Philosophy</h3>
                            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                                In 2021, I was gifted a 3D printer. Thanks to this, I learned how to calibrate, maintain, and use it for projects I would develop later. In my second year of university, I became very interested in electronics and started doing my first experiments on my own with microcontrollers.
                            </p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="relative pl-8 md:pl-12 group">
                            <span class="absolute -left-[9px] top-1 h-5 w-5 rounded-full border-4 border-white dark:border-gray-900 bg-blue-500 group-hover:bg-blue-400 transition-colors"></span>
                            
                            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Education & Experience</h3>
                            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                                I am currently <strong>21 years old</strong> and finishing my <strong>Computer Engineering</strong> degree. One of my best decisions was joining the university's internship program: not only did I improve technically, but I also developed key soft skills working with incredible people.
                            </p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="relative pl-8 md:pl-12 group">
                            <span class="absolute -left-[9px] top-1 h-5 w-5 rounded-full border-4 border-white dark:border-gray-900 bg-orange-500 shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(249,115,22,0.3)]"></span>
                            
                            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">What comes next?</h3>
                            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                                I will start 2026 by joining the <strong>MasOrange</strong> team, thanks to the trust of one of my academic mentors. There, I will develop a Model Context Protocol (MCP) server for integrating language models into their event-driven system.
                            </p>
                            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                                I feel fortunate to have found a vocation that I am passionate about. Computer science allows me to combine logic and creativity to solve problems, and it motivates me to know that in this profession, learning never ends. I am ready for everything that is coming.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                {/* RIGHT COLUMN: STICKY WITH UPDATED STACK */}
                <div class="md:col-span-5 relative">
                    <div class="sticky top-24">
                        <div class="bg-slate-50 dark:bg-gray-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm p-8 rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-xl dark:shadow-blue-900/5 transition-all">
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-8 pb-6 border-b border-slate-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                                <span class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-xl shadow-lg shadow-blue-500/30 text-xl">
                                    üõ†Ô∏è
                                </span>
                                <div>
                                    <h3 class="text-xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">
                                        My Tech Arsenal
                                    </h3>
                                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-gray-400">Stack & Tools</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="space-y-8">
                                {/* GROUP 1: Software Engineering */}
                                <div class="group">
                                    <h4 class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                                        <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue-500"></span> Software Engineering
                                    </h4>
                                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                                        <span class="badge-skill bg-blue-50 text-blue-700 border-blue-200 dark:bg-blue-900/30 dark:text-blue-300 dark:border-blue-800">Java</span>
                                        <span class="badge-skill bg-blue-50 text-blue-700 border-blue-200 dark:bg-blue-900/30 dark:text-blue-300 dark:border-blue-800">SQL / DB Modeling</span>
                                        <span class="badge-skill bg-blue-50 text-blue-700 border-blue-200 dark:bg-blue-900/30 dark:text-blue-300 dark:border-blue-800">Python</span>
                                        <span class="badge-skill bg-blue-50 text-blue-700 border-blue-200 dark:bg-blue-900/30 dark:text-blue-300 dark:border-blue-800">C#</span>
                                        <span class="badge-skill bg-blue-50 text-blue-700 border-blue-200 dark:bg-blue-900/30 dark:text-blue-300 dark:border-blue-800">MVC / Patterns</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                {/* GROUP 2: Systems & Networks */}
                                <div class="group">
                                    <h4 class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                                        <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-indigo-500"></span> Systems & Networks
                                    </h4>
                                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                                        <span class="badge-skill bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700 border-indigo-200 dark:bg-indigo-900/30 dark:text-indigo-300 dark:border-indigo-800">Linux</span>
                                        <span class="badge-skill bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700 border-indigo-200 dark:bg-indigo-900/30 dark:text-indigo-300 dark:border-indigo-800">Docker</span>
                                        <span class="badge-skill bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700 border-indigo-200 dark:bg-indigo-900/30 dark:text-indigo-300 dark:border-indigo-800">Wireshark</span>
                                        <span class="badge-skill bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700 border-indigo-200 dark:bg-indigo-900/30 dark:text-indigo-300 dark:border-indigo-800">Packet Tracer</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                {/* GROUP 3: Maker & Hardware */}
                                <div class="group">
                                    <h4 class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                                        <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-orange-500"></span> Maker & Embedded
                                    </h4>
                                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                                        <span class="badge-skill bg-orange-50 text-orange-700 border-orange-200 dark:bg-orange-900/30 dark:text-orange-300 dark:border-orange-800">Raspberry / ESP32</span>
                                        <span class="badge-skill bg-orange-50 text-orange-700 border-orange-200 dark:bg-orange-900/30 dark:text-orange-300 dark:border-orange-800">C / C++</span>
                                        <span class="badge-skill bg-orange-50 text-orange-700 border-orange-200 dark:bg-orange-900/30 dark:text-orange-300 dark:border-orange-800">SketchUp / 3D</span>
                                        <span class="badge-skill bg-orange-50 text-orange-700 border-orange-200 dark:bg-orange-900/30 dark:text-orange-300 dark:border-orange-800">Hardware</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                {/* GROUP 4: Web Development */}
                                <div class="group">
                                    <h4 class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                                        <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500"></span> Web Development
                                    </h4>
                                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                                        <span class="badge-skill bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-700 border-emerald-200 dark:bg-emerald-900/30 dark:text-emerald-300 dark:border-emerald-800">Astro</span>
                                        <span class="badge-skill bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-700 border-emerald-200 dark:bg-emerald-900/30 dark:text-emerald-300 dark:border-emerald-800">JavaScript</span>
                                        <span class="badge-skill bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-700 border-emerald-200 dark:bg-emerald-900/30 dark:text-emerald-300 dark:border-emerald-800">Tailwind</span>
                                        <span class="badge-skill bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-700 border-emerald-200 dark:bg-emerald-900/30 dark:text-emerald-300 dark:border-emerald-800">Bootstrap</span>
                                        <span class="badge-skill bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-700 border-emerald-200 dark:bg-emerald-900/30 dark:text-emerald-300 dark:border-emerald-800">Primefaces</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <style>
        .badge-skill {
            @apply px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg text-sm font-semibold border transition-all hover:scale-105 cursor-default;
        }
    </style>

</Layout>